      <title>泰国内阁有条件批准赌场合法化法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/thai-cabinet-gives-conditional-nod-for-bill-to-legalize-casinos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国内阁原则上批准了一项旨在使赌场合法化的法案，政府称此举是促进旅游业和打击东南亚国家猖獗的非法赌博行为的重要一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/thai-cabinet-gives-conditional-nod-for-bill-to-legalize-casinos</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 05:31:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
