    <item>
      <title>特朗普和持续的英国脱欧问题共同威胁英国贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/trump-and-ongoing-brexit-troubles-combine-to-threaten-uk-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿咨询集团周一发布的一份报告显示，从 2023 年开始的十年内，英国商品贸易年均增长率预计仅为 0.7%，远低于全球平均水平的 2.9%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/trump-and-ongoing-brexit-troubles-combine-to-threaten-uk-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 05:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥斯汀告诉 OMB 需要 9260 亿美元的国防预算，比当前计划多出 550 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/austin-on-exit-sees-need-for-nearly-a-trillion-dollars-in-defense-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将离任的国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀建议美国政府将 2026 财年的国防开支增加约 500 亿美元，这一增幅将使五角大楼的预算在未来几年内超过 1 万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/austin-on-exit-sees-need-for-nearly-a-trillion-dollars-in-defense-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 05:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
